</figure>

<p>I&rsquo;ve also used it to proofread some blog posts, write unit tests, and to bootstrap a repo that stands up a two-tower model for recommendations just to see what the agent would do with a blank slate. Here&rsquo;s what it generated, which was pretty basic but still beyond the scope of anything I would have thought possible last year:
