<p>None of these are groundbreaking tasks (again, a lot of personalized Google/docs lookups), and working on them does give my GPUs and RAM a workout and the K-V cache grows to 64 GB RAM.</p>
<figure><img src="https://vickiboykis.com/images/gemma_gpu.png" width="600">
